700944f-a.title: Bronx: Tremont Avenue (East - Fink Avenue
700944f-a.text:
East Tremont Ave., east side, south from Fink to Westchester
Aves. The G.W. Bromley map of 1927 designates the above houses
with the numbers 70 to 80,on what appears to be Westchester Square.
A portion of the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park
subway line is visible on the extreme right.
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
